### =====================================================================
### Accounting API  (base route: api/accounting/)
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Report - full range for a user
POST {{host}}/api/accounting/Report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "fromDate": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2026-07-05T00:00:00Z"
}

### Report - no filters (all)
POST {{host}}/api/accounting/Report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}"
}
